<img alt="" src="https://www.patriotprivacy.com/wp-content/themes/OptimizePress1.65/timthumb.php?src=http://www.patriotprivacy.com/wp-content/uploads/enhanced-5869-1401481919-2.jpg&h=144&w=144&zc=1" style="border:1px solid #c0c0c0;margin:0 20px 10px 0;" align="left">
