<div class="postpic">
<img alt="" src="https://www.patriotprivacy.com/wp-content/themes/OptimizePress1.65/timthumb.php?src=http://www.patriotprivacy.com/wp-content/uploads/6a00d83451b71f69e20147e2757276970b-400wi.jpg&h=144&w=144&zc=1" style="border:1px solid #c0c0c0;margin:0 20px 10px 0;" align="left">
