<h2 class="postinfoheader"><a href="http://www.patriotprivacy.com/your-latest-newsletter-is-here-2/">Your latest newsletter is here&#8230;</a></h2>

                  <div class="post-meta">
                    
                    <p class="post-people" style="font-size:13px !important;">Posted In <a href="http://www.patriotprivacy.com/category/society/" rel="category tag">Patriot Privacy &amp; Security Society</a>, <a href="http://www.patriotprivacy.com/category/privacy-alert/" rel="category tag">Privacy Alert</a>, <a href="http://www.patriotprivacy.com/category/security-alert/" rel="category tag">Security Alert</a> 
                                        <span class="divide">|</span> No comments  </p>
                    </div>

<p>Here is the second edition of the Patriot Privacy and Security Society Newsletter.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;">Just click here to access it. </span></span></span></p>
<p>You can save it by clicking on the link and then right click on the page and clicking save.</p>
<p>This edition contains all of the advisories we published in September after you received your first newsletter in mid-September. For that reason, there is one less article than there normally will be in a regular month.</p>
<p>Starting with next month’s newsletter, the newsletter will contain all the material we published in that particular month.</p>
<p>Please feel free to share the newsletter and, as always, you can write me at<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;"> <span style="color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;">Rob@PatriotPrivacy.com</span></span></span></p>
<p>Be safe and secure,</p>
<p>Rob Douglas</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>


